	<p>ADDME</p>
	
	<definition>
	<title>ADDME</title>
	<statement>
		<p>The <term>angular momentum</term> of a rigid object about a given axis is the product of the object's moment of inertia and angular velocity about that axis: <me>\vec{L} = I\vec{\omega}</me></p>
	</statement>
</definition>

  
